      "avalancheActivity": {
        "comment": "V Jesen\u00edk\u00e1ch v 1300 m/m le\u017e\u00ed okolo 40 cm sn\u011bhu, na h\u0159ebeni hor do 10 cm.\r\nV lavinov\u00fdch svaz\u00edch je sn\u011bhu m\u00edsty ulo\u017eeno v\u00edce. \r\nSn\u011bhov\u00e1 vrstva je stabiln\u00ed. \r\nNa povrchu le\u017e\u00ed 2cm ledov\u00e1 krusta.\r\nV Jesen\u00edk\u00e1ch plat\u00ed 1. lavinov\u00fd stupe\u0148.\r\n"
